<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">If you&apos;ve read &quot;Blackout&quot;, I would go ahead and read &quot;All Clear&quot; next, because the stories are more closely linked than either one are to &quot;Doomsday&quot;. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">If you've read "Blackout", I would go ahead and read "All Clear" next, because the stories are more closely linked than either one are to "Doomsday". But do read "Doomsday"; it's excellent.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
